Privacy Policy – School Attendance App

Effective Date: 10/15/2025

School Attendance App (“we”, “our”, or “us”) values the privacy of our users (“you” or “your”) and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our School Attendance App (“App”). By using our App, you agree to the practices described in this policy.

1. Information We Collect

We may collect the following types of information:

a. Personal Information:

Student name, class, and roll number

Parent/guardian name and contact information

Teacher or staff name and contact information

b. Usage Information:

Attendance records

Login credentials (username,)

App usage activity (e.g., features used, login times)

c. Device Information:

Device type, operating system, and app version

IP address

2. How We Use Your Information

Your information may be used for:

Recording and managing student attendance

Communicating important school updates and announcements

Personalizing the user experience

Improving app functionality and performance

Compliance with legal obligations

3. Sharing of Information

We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. Information may be shared:

With authorized school staff and teachers for attendance and communication purposes

To comply with legal obligations or protect rights

With third-party service providers that assist in app operations (e.g., cloud storage), under strict confidentiality

4. Data Security

We implement industry-standard measures to protect your information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of electronic storage or transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.

5. Data Retention

We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy or as required by law.

6. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access your personal data

Correct any inaccurate information

Request deletion of your personal data, subject to legal and operational requirements

To exercise these rights, contact us at: schoolattendanceapp@gmail.com

7. Children’s Privacy

Our app is designed for school use, and we take extra care to protect children’s information. We collect personal data of students only with parental/guardian consent.

8. Third-Party Links

Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties.

9. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be communicated within the app and updated with a new effective date.

10. Contact Us

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how your data is handled, please contact us:

Email:  schoolattendanceapp@gmail.com
Address: Dolakha, Nepal 
